articles.author: Emilee Speck, Scott Sistek
articles.title: Ax-3 astronaut crew splashes down off Florida after storms delay return home for nearly a week - Fox Weather
articles.description: After spending an extra six days in space because of stormy weather near Florida, the first all-European private astronaut mission returned home to Earth early Friday morning, splashing down off the Florida coast.
